---
title: SuperQuick Biriyani-Inspired Turkey  with Cumin-Turmeric Rice and Yogurt Sauce
description: Ground turkey is cooked with warm Indian-inspired spices and paired with buttery cumin-turmeric rice for this quick and delicious dinner. Cilantro, crispy shallots and a drizzle of yogurt sauce are the perfect finishing touches.

